  "texts": [
    "For all three analyses, we focus on the medium-value data condition.",
    "until they do so.",
    "The results of this exercise are presented in plots iii) of Panel A and Panel B in Figure 6.",
    "The results are nearly identical to the case with risk-loving agents, and we see that exploration (unsurprisingly) increases monotonically with the number of explorative agents.",
    "This completes our extensions to the original streetlight experiment using GABE."
  ]
